flowchart LR
    C[Client] --> I[Ingest API\nPOST /ingest/:schema_id]
    I --> R[Schema Registry]
    R --> A[Analyzer]
    A --> K[Classifier]
    K --> S[Storage Strategy Generator]
    S --> Q[CRUD Planner / Executor]

    Q --> SQL[(MySQL)]
    Q --> M[(MongoDB)]
    SQL --> G[Result Aggregator]
    M --> G
    G --> O[Unified JSON Response]
    O --> C
